{
  "stem": "19921.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You had-- few ra-- [INAUDIBLE] passenger trains, and then-- then were radio transport trains.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was not, you know, secluded, and neither was-- they had already facilities there, and the doors were not shut.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You didn't have to beg the KBG guy to open up, give his water, something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You were free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You didn't have any provision.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Was on your own.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got provisions strictly-- not for money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For money, they didn't want to have any money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The peasants did not want any money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't have nothing to do with the money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They couldn't buy anything for the money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you traded things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You traded things.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The business commodity was like matches, tobacco-- none of them-- none of those people smoked at that time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Tobacco, matches, and salt, and, of course, clothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So whatever we had, we traded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's how we got the bread, and water, and whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the trip itself to Tashkent took close to two weeks-- close to two weeks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in one of those nights when we went for trading-- usually they-- the-- the conductor, whoever it was, that announced that the-- or the engineer announced, the train would stop here for two hours, refueling, whatever it-- or three hours, sometimes even longer.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this time, they announced that the-- the train would stop for two hours, or two and 1/2 hours.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we went for two and a half hours, myself and my-- myself and my brother not to trade things in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Myself and my brother-in-law to trade in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Meanwhile, we got back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The train was gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The train was gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, we had-- each train had a railroad-- had a-- a Red Cross car.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had special markings.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
